name: House Finch
overview: House finches move slow and the sit still as they shell seeds by crushing them with rapid bites. Their flight is bouncy.
habitat: House Finches can collect at feeders, and also like to perch high in nearby trees. You can find them in backyards, urban centers, farms, forests, deserts and grasslands.
